Subject: ACPI: platform_profile: Make sure all profile handlers agree on
 profile
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
Git-commit: e836b7dfbabaa9d8a99b58ef0afa586f782d8e01
